Load libraries

library(tidyverse)
library(dismo)
library(raster)
library(sp)
library(sf)

Import and process environmental data

env_list <- dir("data/wc_env_data/", pattern = ".tif", full.names = TRUE)
env_stack <- raster::stack(env_list)
plot(env_stack)

utmproj <- "+proj=utm +zone=34 +south +datum=WGS84 +units=m +no_defs"
env_stack <- projectRaster(env_stack, crs = utmproj)
plot(env_stack)

var_reduced <- usdm::vifcor(env_stack, th=0.6) 
var_reduced@results$Variables

# Exclude the collinear variables that were identified in the previous step
env_stack<- usdm::exclude(env_stack,var_reduced)

  dplyr::filter(PR_NAME == "WESTERN CAPE") %>% 
  st_transform(crs = utmproj)

Import and process species data

spp_occ <- read_csv("data/spp_data/Breviceps montanus.csv") %>% 
  st_as_sf(., coords = c("decimalLongitude", "decimalLatitude"), crs = latlongCRS) %>% 
  st_transform(crs = utmproj)

nrow(spp_occ)
[1] 771
spp_occ <- spp_occ %>% 
  distinct(geometry, .keep_all = TRUE)

nrow(spp_occ)
[1] 372
ggplot()+
  geom_sf(data = wc)+
  geom_sf(data = spp_occ)+
  coord_sf(datum = utmproj)

spp_occ <- st_intersection(spp_occ, wc)

ggplot()+
  geom_sf(data = wc)+
  geom_sf(data = spp_occ)+
  coord_sf(datum = utmproj)

Pseudo-absence points

n_points <- 10000

bck_points <- st_sample(wc, n_points) %>% 
  st_sf() # returns sfc object - use st_sf() to convert to sf

## Base R plots
plot(env_stack[[1]])
plot(wc$geometry, add = TRUE)
plot(bck_points, cex = 0.5, add = TRUE)
plot(spp_occ$geometry, cex = 1, add = TRUE, col = "red")

## Better plots with rasterVis::levelplot
p <- rasterVis::levelplot(env_stack[[1]], 
                     main= "Presence and background points - Breviceps montanus",xlab = "Latitude",ylab = "Longitude",
                     contour = FALSE, 
                     margin = FALSE,
                     col.regions = rev(terrain.colors(40)))+
  latticeExtra::layer(sp.points(as(bck_points$geometry,"Spatial"), pch = 19, cex = 0.2, col = "blue"))+
  latticeExtra::layer(sp.points(as(spp_occ$geometry,"Spatial"), pch = 19, cex = 0.8, col = "black"))+
  latticeExtra::layer(sp.lines(as(wc$geometry, "Spatial"), lwd = 2.5, col = "black"))

p

Build Maxent model

# Withold a 10% sample of occ points for testing the model
fold <- kfold(spp_occ, k=10)
occtest <- spp_occ[fold == 1, ]
occtrain <- spp_occ[fold != 1, ]

# Convert to spatialpointsdataframe 
occtest <- as(occtest, "Spatial")
occtrain <- as(occtrain, "Spatial")
bck_points <- as(bck_points, "Spatial")

Run maxent

spp_ME <- dismo::maxent(
  x = env_stack, 
  p = occtrain,  
  a = bck_points,
  removeDuplicates=TRUE, 
  path = paste0(getwd(),"/data/SDM results"), 
  args = c("randomtestpoints=30", "betamultiplier=1", 
           "linear=true", 
           "quadratic=true", "product=true", "threshold=true", 
           "hinge=true", "threads=2", "responsecurves=true", 
           "jackknife=true","askoverwrite=false"))

Model evaluation

eval_me <- dismo::evaluate(spp_ME, x = env_stack, p = occtest, a = bck_points)

Predict - probability surface

spp_predict <- dismo::predict(spp_ME, env_stack, progress = "") 

p <- rasterVis::levelplot(spp_predict, 
                     main= "Predicted probability surface - Breviceps montanus SDM",xlab = "Latitude",ylab = "Longitude",
                     contour = FALSE, 
                     margin = FALSE,
                     col.regions = rev(terrain.colors(40)))+
  latticeExtra::layer(sp.points(as(spp_occ$geometry,"Spatial"), pch = 19, cex = 0.8, col = "black"))+
  latticeExtra::layer(sp.lines(as(wc$geometry, "Spatial"), lwd = 2.5, col = "black"))

p

Predict - binary surface

threshold(eval_me)
# A tibble: 1 x 6
  kappa spec_sens no_omission prevalence equal_sens_spec sensitivity
  <dbl>     <dbl>       <dbl>      <dbl>           <dbl>       <dbl>
1 0.931     0.204      0.0607    0.00350           0.240       0.218
mSSS <- threshold(eval_me)[["spec_sens"]]

mSSS_matrix <- matrix(c(0,mSSS,0, # c(from, to, conversion_value)
                        mSSS,1,1), 
                      ncol=3, byrow=TRUE)

binary_prediction <- reclassify(spp_predict, mSSS_matrix)

p <- rasterVis::levelplot(binary_prediction, 
                     main= "Predicted binary surface - Breviceps montanus SDM",xlab = "Latitude",ylab = "Longitude",
                     contour = FALSE, 
                     margin = FALSE,
                     col.regions = rev(terrain.colors(40)))+
  latticeExtra::layer(sp.points(as(spp_occ$geometry,"Spatial"), pch = 19, cex = 0.8, col = "black"))+
  latticeExtra::layer(sp.lines(as(wc$geometry, "Spatial"), lwd = 2.5, col = "black"))

p

Write SDM raster

raster::writeRaster(spp_predict, 
                    filename = ("data/SDM results/spp_occSDM.tif"), 
                    format="GTiff", 
                    overwrite=TRUE)

Write workspace and map

save.image("data/SDM results/SDM_workspace.RData")
